    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> divina providente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rege[s</rs>. Regum pri]ncipumque dignitatem in hoc
                        fulciri cognoscimus, si iustis suorum fidelium petitionibus adsensum
                        prebuerit. Quocirca omnium fidelium sanctae Dei Aecclesie nostrorumque
                        presentium ac futuroru[m devotio] noverit, qualiter <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >interventu ac petitione</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Count #fidelisOf"><name ref="Lanfrancus"
                                >Lanfranci</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Count #fidelisOf"><name ref="Alderamus"
                                >Aledrammi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitum</rs> dilector[um] nostrorum <rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >fidelium</rs> per hoc nostrum preceptum donamus atque largimur
                            <persName key="#Countess"><name ref="Rotruda/Roza"
                            >Rotrude</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Countess">comitisse</rs>, que [Roza vocatur, et] <persName
                            key="#Count"><name ref="Elisardus">Elisiardo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comiti</rs> atque <persName
                            key="#legallyRecognisedUnionWith #daughterOf"><name ref="Rodelinda"
                                >Rotlinde</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#legallyRecognisedUnionWith">uxori</rs> sue et <rs
                            key="#daughterOf">filie</rs> nostre <rs key="#Fiscal_property">quasdam
                            res iuri regni nostri quondam pertinentes</rs>, positas in <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/306">Terdonensi</geogName> in locis
                        et <rs key="#Fundi">fundis</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Inheritance #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/2402">Garbanigo</geogName>, <geogName
                                key="#Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Inheritance #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                                ref="#estates2401">Petra Nigra</geogName>, <geogName
                                    key="#Natural_landscape #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Inflow #Inheritance #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                                    ref="#estates/2400"><placeName ref="#places/2792"
                            >Besemuntio</placeName></geogName>, nec non et <rs key="#Mills">tria
                            molendina</rs> iuxta <placeName ref="#places/65">Ticinensem
                            urbem</placeName> in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio Catarona</rs> prope <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs> quod <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/129">Deodote</orgName> dicitur, simul cum <rs
                            key="#Areas">areis terre</rs> et <rs key="#Curtes">corticulis</rs> atque
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> positis ubi extant ipsa
                        molendina, sicut hactenus a nobis detenta sunt. Predictas igitur res atque
                        molendina <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >de iure regni et nostro in prefatorum hominum nostrorum fidelium</rs>
                        ius et dominium omnino transfundimus ac delegamus una cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Mills"
                        >molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains"
                            >alpibus</rs>, <rs key="#Natural_landscape">planitiebus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumve decursibus</rs> et cum omnibus que dici
                        vel nominari possunt, <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs> ad
                        ipsas res aspitientibus in integrum, statuentes ut si quis ex supradictis
                        Rotruda et Elisiardo atque Rotlinda vivendo alteri superstes fuerit, de
                        supradictis rebus sibi invicem <rs key="#Inflow #Inheritance">hereditario
                            iure</rs> succedant, habeantque potestatem tenendi, donandi, vendendi,
                        commutandi, pro anima [i]udicandi, vel quicquid eorum decreverit animus
                        faciendi, omnium hominum contradictione remota. Si quis igitur huius
                        nostr[i] precepti violator exstiterit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">[au]ri optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem kamere nostre</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem prefatis nostris
                            fidelibus suorumque heredibus</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur
                        diligentiusque ab omnibus observetur, [m]anibus propriis roborantes anulo
                        nostro insigniri iussimus. Signa serenissimorum (MF) (MF) Hugonis et
                        Lotharii regum. <persName key="#Chancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1535"
                            >Giseprandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> et <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs>
                        ad vicem <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1531"
                            >Bosonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi (SR) (SI D). Data IIII
                        kal. aprilis, anno dominic[e] incarnationis DCCCCXLV, regni vero domni
                        Hug[onis XV]IIII, Lotharii XIIII, indictione tertia. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName>. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
